        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. Value of production quantity (unit) is retrieved from EuroStat for the year 2019, accessed on 20231010. Production quantity is 2'577'423'791 units multiplied by the 4 kg/unit of clay roof tile.

Reference production quantity: "Non-refractory clay roofing tiles", EUROPEAN UNION (28), PRODQNT.
Industry, trade and services&gt;Statistics on the production of manufactured foods (prom)&gt;Sold production, exports and imports (ds-056120). Retrieved from: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/DS-056120__custom_7772056/default/table?lang=en

Reference weight per unit of clay roof tile: ecoinvent v2 Report 7, Buildings, Part IV, p. 25. Presumed weight per tile: 4 kg.</productionVolumeComment>
